node_modules
prebuilt_lockfile.json
# ...except the signer plugin modules, which commit their lockfile as source
# (an empty list `[]`) so the module can be built from source — e.g. from the
# offline BCR the //e2e/sbom integration test resolves them through. The real
# release digests are produced hermetically by Bazel (the signer_*_dist_tar
# targets in //img/private/release bake the populated lockfile into the released
# source archive), never touching the working tree.
!modules/rules_img_signer_cosign/prebuilt_lockfile.json
!modules/rules_img_signer_notation/prebuilt_lockfile.json
tools/bazel
e2e/*/tools/bazel
